cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a method for object detection and geolocation using street view imagery, which involves computer vision and robotics (cs.CV and cs.RO). The method uses fully convolutional neural networks (cs.AI) and a custom Markov Random Field model (cs.LG) for triangulation. The paper also discusses the application of the method in urban planning and asset monitoring (cs.GR).
